<tool id="gigaword.get" name="Get" version="1.0.0">
 <description>
  Retreive a single document from the Gigaword Datasource.
 </description>
 <command interpreter="lsd">
  get.lsd $token $key $service $output
 </command>
 <inputs>
  <param format="oauth" label="OAuth Token" name="token" type="data">
  </param>
  <param label="Document ID" name="key" type="text" value="AFP_ENG_19940512.0001">
  </param>
  <param label="Language" name="service" type="select">
  </param>
  <option value="GWENDataSource">
   English
  </option>
  <option value="GWZHDataSource">
   Chinese
  </option>
  <option value="GWESDataSource">
   Spanish
  </option>
  <option value="GWARDataSource">
   Arabic
  </option>
 </inputs>
 <outputs>
  <data format="ldc" name="output">
  </data>
 </outputs>
 <help>
  `_

To obtain an OAuth token visit the link above and log in with your LDC id and password. Then paste
the OAuth token into the above field.

]]&gt;
  License
-------

ask Chris
 </help>
</tool>